{
  "text": ", is closely related to 1 6 times the LHS of the inequality of the Szpiro conjecture for E \u03bb , since the degree of the pull-back to P 1 of the divisor at infinity of the natural compactification of M ell \u2297 Q is 6 times 1 = the degree of \u03c9 C (D), see [CITATION_1] .",
